title: AnyDVD HD 7.6.9.0
description:
7.6.9.0 2016 02 14
- New (Blu-ray): Support for new discs
- New (DVD): Support for new discs
- Change: Installer signed with SHA256 certificate
- Note: On Windows Vista and Server 2008, Update 2763674 must be installed.
        See https://support.microsoft.com/en-us/kb/2763674
- Fix (Blu-ray): Crash with certain discs
- Some minor fixes and improvements


Trully LAST release, untouched
